This part of the application will be further developed, so you have more information about who you have referred and rewards payments that have been made to you and are due to you. 

How do I get paid

Rewards are credited to your account within 30 days of the referred customer's first payment.  Your payment details on your account must be up to date to receive referral payments.. 

Do I need to be an organisation to be a referrer?

Either organisations or individuals can take advantage of the referral scheme.  Referrers just need to have a customer account on Accessible Surveys, with up to date payment details.

How do organisations I refer to Accessible Surveys receive their discount?

When an organisation creates a customer account on Accessible Surveys using your ‘Referral Link’.
